<item> <xref ReadAMessageTA>
<item> <xref ComposingMessagesTA>
<\list>

<s2 id=MAttach>Mailer Attachment List

	<idx>Attachment list<sort>attachment list<\idx>

If you receive a mail message containing one or more attachments,
the Attachment list will appear in the main window.  Also, the
Compose window displays the Attachment list.

You can add attachments to outgoing mail messages, save attachments 
in files, open attachments, select all the attachments, run executable 
files, or print attachments.

<newline>&empty;
<figure nonumber entity=MAttachList>
<\figure>
<newline>&empty;

<procedure>See Also
<list bullet tight>
<!--<item> <xref MAttachMenu>-->
