	<idx>Save a copy of outgoing mail in, in Mailer Basic Options dialog box<sort>save a copy of outgoing mail in, in mailer basic options dialog box<\idx>
    <idx>Mailbox for outgoing mail, in Basic Options dialog box<sort>mailbox for outgoing mail, in basic options dialog box<\idx>
<!--
	<idx>Signal new mail with, in Mailer Basic Options dialog box<sort>signal new mail with, in mailer basic options dialog box<\idx>
