	<idx>Display headers, in Mailer Basic Options dialog box<sort>display headers, in mailer basic options dialog box<\idx>
	<idx>Show To recipient when mail is from me, in Mailer Basic Options dialog box<sort>show to recipient when mail is from me, in mailer basic options dialog box<\idx>
	<idx>Display message numbers, in Mailer Basic Options dialog box<sort>display message numbers, in mailer basic options dialog box<\idx>
	<idx>Destroy Deleted Messages, in Mailer Basic Options dialog box<sort>destroy deleted messages, in mailer basic options dialog box<\idx>
