<s1 id=ToolbarOptions>Mailer Toolbar Options Dialog Box

	<idx>Toolbar Options dialog box, reference<sort>toolbar options dialog 
box<\idx>
	<idx>Show Buttons As, in Toolbar Options dialog box<sort>show buttons as, 
in toolbar options dialog box<\idx>
	<idx>Commands, in Toolbar Options dialog box<sort>commands, in toolbar 
options dialog box<\idx>
	<idx>Add, in Toolbar Options dialog box<sort>add, in toolbar options 
dialog box<\idx>
	<idx>Remove, in Toolbar Options dialog box<sort>remove, in toolbar options 
