option to respond to incoming mail messages.

<newline>&empty;
<figure nonumber entity=Mailer-Vacation>
<\figure>
<newline>&empty;

<!--
<term nogloss>Vacation Precedence = junk
<\term> 
<list plain tight>
<item>This line tells the mail delivery agent to set this mail
to a lower priority and not to return any error messages generated by
